snippet.title: Paleo Pines - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Welcome to Paleo Pines, a quaint and quirky island populated by charming dinosaurs and welcoming townsfolk. We hope you enjoy your time with us on the island as you fix up your ranch to make a patch of paradise your very own. But as you'll soon experience, your time at Paleo Pines involves a mystery to uncover - there are wild dinosaurs to tame, after all, and with your trusty Parasaurolophus, Lucky, it's up to you to uncover the lost history of the island.

Paleo Pines is coming to PC, PlayStation 4 & 5, Xbox Series X|S, Xbox One and Nintendo Switch digitally and physically this fall from Modus Games and developer Italic Pig. Wishlist: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1202200/Paleo_Pines/

Learn more here: https://www.paleopines.com
